Package org.openwms.wms.movements.api

Enum Class MovementType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MovementType>
org.openwms.wms.movements.api.MovementType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MovementType>, Constable
public enum MovementType extends Enum<MovementType>
A MovementType defines all possible types of Movements in a project. Each Movement must be of a specific type.
Author:
Heiko Scherrer
